      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong> then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Chop your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> roughly</p><p>Combine your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> – this is your <strong>balsamic dressing</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>salad</strong> and <strong>chopped tomato</strong> to the dressing and toss – this is your <strong>balsamic salad</strong></p>",
